{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_04_03",
  "title": "kana 3話 ストッキングを被った顔",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（そうこうするうち、打ち合わせや稽古の期間も過ぎて）\n（映画の撮影が始まった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（As time went on‚ the period of meetings and rehearsals passed‚）\n（and filming for the movie began.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.8396145184
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "いけん。結局、一睡も出来んかったのぉ。今日は\n大事な仕事があるけぇ、わくわくして眠れんかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't. In the end‚ I couldn't get a wink of sleep. Today‚\nI couldn't sleep because I'm so excited about the important work I have to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.8314762752
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "荷物は……爆弾、毒針、バナナ……\nおやつは三百円までじゃな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Luggage… bombs‚ poison needles‚ bananas…\nSnacks are up to $3.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "よっしゃ、今日も張り切ってお仕置きするけん！\nちゃーんとお家に帰ってくるまでが仕事じゃからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ I'm going to punish you with all my might today!\nMy job's not done until you get home safely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.6000020345,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3975.1482646000013,
          "startTime": 34.5751502991
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.5751502991
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "って、なんじゃあの車！　こっちに向かってきとる\nいけん、いけんぞーーー！　ぶつかるうぅぅぅ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What the―― That car! It's coming straight for me!\nOh no‚ oh no~~~! We're gonna crashhhh!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.1666692098,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9648.707389799994,
          "startTime": 44.2238576889
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_ball-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10175.3739993,
          "startTime": 44.7505242984
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_light-down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10142.040665899998,
          "startTime": 44.717190965
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.2238576889
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.5505227726
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（さすがkanaさんだな）\n（結局、昨日までずっと役に文句言ってたとは思えない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She really is kana-san.）\n（You wouldn't believe she was complaining about her role until yesterday.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.8333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.8991157533
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "……ふんふん。kanaが予想以上にハマってるから\nもっと派手な演出を入れてやってみたいと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hmm hmm. Since kana's fitting in better than expected‚\nI want to try adding some more flashy direction.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.6666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、kanaがショックで髪ぜ～んぶ抜けて\n頭つるっつるになるシーンを入れるんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ you're adding a scene where kana's hair falls out from shock\nand she goes completely bald.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.8000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.3581183118
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "さっすが監督！　原作だと一コマだけのネタですけど\n妥協しないで、全部やりきるんですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected of the director! In the original‚ it's just a one-panel gag‚\nbut you're not compromising and going all out!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.0000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.9981237731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、大丈夫です！！\n監督のご期待に応えられるよう、頑張ります！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ it's fine!!\nI'll do my best to meet your expectations!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.8666748047,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pillow-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5536.984284900001,
          "startTime": 84.4036590896
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pillow-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7533.325195300009,
          "startTime": 86.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.5369924229
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.5369924229
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "ふざっけんな、あのおっさん！！\nこっちが下手に出てりゃあ調子に乗りやがって！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kidding me‚ you old geezer!!\nYou're getting cocky because I'm being nice!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.7666748047,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pillow-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5833.325195299992,
          "startTime": 93.6
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pillow-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9333.32519529999,
          "startTime": 97.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "その場の思いつきで何度も台本書き換えんな！\nしかもkanaにクソダサいヅラまで被らせるし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't rewrite the script over and over again on the spur of the moment!\nAnd you made kana wear this stupid wig!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.800008138,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pillow-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9333.325195300005,
          "startTime": 104.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.4506240211
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "おまけに被らせておいて、「やっぱ違った」\nってどういうことだよ！　やり損じゃんか！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then after you put it on me‚ you say‚ \"Actually‚ I changed my mind\"?\nWhat's that supposed to mean?! It was all for nothing!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.5852184499,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pillow-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4178.238180600005,
          "startTime": 105.7634566305
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pillow-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6181.448216800007,
          "startTime": 107.7666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pillow-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8448.114883400009,
          "startTime": 110.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.3032100362
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "か、kanaさん、落ち着いて……\nさすがに備品のぬいぐるみを殴るのはマズいんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "k-kana-san‚ calm down…\nIt's not okay to hit the stuffed animals that are part of the props…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.966675822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "は？　備品じゃないし\nkanaが自分で持ってきたの、文句ある？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? It's not a prop.\nI brought it myself. You got a problem with that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.0000152589,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pillow-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4333.318074399997,
          "startTime": 119.3333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pillow-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7899.984741099999,
          "startTime": 122.9
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pillow-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9549.98474109999,
          "startTime": 124.55
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.8021051409
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "どうせ最悪の撮影になるのは分かってたし\nストレス解消しないと、メンタルがもつ気しないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew this was going to be the worst shoot ever‚\nand I don't think I can handle it mentally if I don't relieve some stress.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.4000152589,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pillow-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5166.651407800004,
          "startTime": 127.5666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pillow-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6898.265234200011,
          "startTime": 129.2982804931
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pillow-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9099.984741100001,
          "startTime": 131.5
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10699.984741099996,
          "startTime": 133.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "問題は……なくはない気もしますけど……\nまぁ、他の人に見られなければいいか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There might… be a problem…\nWell‚ as long as nobody else sees it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.8000152589,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3449.255085099992,
          "startTime": 134.249270344
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.249270344
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　あぁ、すみません、呼びに来ていただいて\nkanaさん、そろそろ出番だそうです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? Oh‚ sorry for making you come get me.\nkana-san‚ it's almost time for your scene!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.1000152589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_03-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました～、すぐスタジオ戻りま～す……\n……え？　落とし穴にハマるシーンを撮りたい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ I'll be right back to the studio…\n…Huh? You want to film a scene where I fall into a pitfall?",
        "id": ""
